OL,3,CHealth bosses welcome Trust being
OL,4,Cplaced 120th out of 134 in national
OL,5,Crankings
OL,7,FThe NHS trust which runs hospitals in
OL,8,Fnorth and west Cumbria has made what
OL,9,Fbosses describe as 'significant
OL,10,Fpositive progress' despite being
OL,11,Fgraded among the worst performers
OL,12,Facross England.
OL,14,FTrusts are ranked in NHS league tables
OL,15,Fand the latest National Oversight
OL,16,FFramework (NOF) ratings place North
OL,17,FCumbria Integrated Care NHS Foundation
OL,18,FTrust (NCIC) 120th out of 134 - a rise
OL,19,Fof 10 places since the previous
OL,20,Fresults.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
