OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1781470069
OL,3,CHealth bosses welcome Trust being
OL,4,Cplaced 120th out of 134 in national
OL,5,Crankings
OL,7,FThe trust says the improvement
OL,8,Freflects its strengthened performance
OL,9,Facross planned care, diagnostics and
OL,10,FReferral to Treatment (RTT) pathways.
OL,12,FNCIC Chief Executive Trudie Davies
OL,13,Fsaid: "The plans we have developed
OL,14,Ftogether are taking us in the right
OL,15,Fdirection.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,327,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1781470069
OL,3,CHealth bosses welcome Trust being
OL,4,Cplaced 120th out of 134 in national
OL,5,Crankings
OL,7,F"It is good to see that the hard work
OL,8,Fof our staff is beginning to pay off
OL,9,Fin terms of performance. They should
OL,10,Fbe very proud of what they are
OL,11,Fachieving. This is not just about
OL,12,Fnumbers, it is about the quality of
OL,13,Fcare we provide for our patients, and
OL,14,Fthat is what matters to us most.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,327,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1781470069
OL,3,CHealth bosses welcome Trust being
OL,4,Cplaced 120th out of 134 in national
OL,5,Crankings
OL,7,F"Our waiting times for elective care
OL,8,Fare much improved, but we know we
OL,9,Fstill have much more to do. Our
OL,10,Fpatients still wait too long in our
OL,11,Femergency departments, but we are
OL,12,Fconfident that our #4m investment in
OL,13,Fstaffing and facilities will create
OL,14,Fthe right environment for us to
OL,15,Fprovide the best possible care."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
